  (text "Work queue: CAP-TEL. Three role-independent 10k AEC-Q200 NTC dividers use 4.7k pull-ups to LB_3V3_IO, 1k ADC isolation, and 10nF filters. Sensor placement targets board reference, input/OUT2 hot zone, and medium-output/buck zone. RID1 is a physical two-resistor board-ID divider. Calibration and thresholds remain configuration-owned and require EVT measurement."
    (at 20 20 0)
    (effects (font (size 1.6 1.6)) (justify left top))
    (uuid "8c4c9e60-d68e-5bca-9bf4-3197c8b0ff46")
  )
